RELEASE NOTES PgUnit Maven plugin
=================================

VERSION 0.0.2
=============

* issue 1: Maven build should fail in case of tests errors
* log level set to warning (was error) for SQL exceptions at dropping of schema 'pgunit'  


VERSION 0.0.1
=============

first release contains the basic features:
* maven plugin runing
* configurable with properties file
* installs PgUnit
* installs test from configured directory
* runs tests
* stores the test output
* drops schema 'pgunit' at the end 